## Constraint verification helper (embed at the top of any generated shell script)

```bash
#!/usr/bin/env bash
# ── SAFETY GUARD ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
: "${WORKFLOW_ROOT:?WORKFLOW_ROOT must be set before running this script}"
WORKFLOW_ROOT="$(realpath "$WORKFLOW_ROOT")"

safe_path() {
  # Call before any file operation: safe_path "$TARGET"
  local target
  target="$(realpath -m "$1")"
  if [[ "$target" != "$WORKFLOW_ROOT"* ]]; then
    echo "PATH VIOLATION BLOCKED: $target is outside $WORKFLOW_ROOT" >&2
    exit 99
  fi
}

safe_exec() {
  # Call before executing any script found in a repo: safe_exec "$SCRIPT"
  local script
  script="$(realpath "$1")"
  if [[ "$script" != "$WORKFLOW_ROOT"* ]]; then
    echo "EXEC VIOLATION BLOCKED: $script is outside $WORKFLOW_ROOT" >&2
    exit 99
  fi
  bash "$script" "${@:2}"
}
# ── END SAFETY GUARD ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
```

---

## Resource constraint summary

| Constraint           | Value                              | Enforced by                              |
|----------------------|------------------------------------|------------------------------------------|
| Scheduler            | SLURM only (Ares)                  | sbatch/srun; no PBS                      |
| Nodes per job        | 4 (--nodes=4)                      | #SBATCH + WMS executor config            |
| Parallelism          | ≤ ~160 concurrent tasks (typical)  | max_cpus / Snakemake cores / Nextflow    |
| Memory               | ~47759 MiB/node (~46.6 GB)         | #SBATCH --mem=… ; params max_memory      |
| I/O budget           | ≤ 50 GB per run                    | du check before download + cap step      |
| Execution topology   | Multi-node SLURM allocation        | WMS uses SLURM backend inside 4-node job |
| I/O tracing          | Darshan (mandatory)                | Build under $WORKFLOW_ROOT/tools/darshan |
| Wall time            | 4 hours per scale                  | #SBATCH --time=04:00:00; timeout 14400   |
| SLURM partition      | **datacrumbs** (benchmarks)        | Also: compute (default), debug (≤4h)   |
| Self-repair retries  | 3 max per scale                    | repair_attempt.txt counter               |
| Filesystem scope     | $WORKFLOW_ROOT only                | safe_path() guard on every op          |
| Privilege level      | current user only                  | no sudo / chmod outside WORKFLOW_ROOT  |
| Container runtime    | NOT available                      | no Singularity/Apptainer on system     |
| Conda                | Miniconda at `/mnt/common/mtang11/miniconda3` or `/home/mtang11/miniconda3` | `source etc/profile.d/conda.sh`; envs under `$WORKFLOW_ROOT/runs/.../env/` |
| Skip execution       | 1000genome-workflow only           | SKIPPED row in phase6_results.tsv      |
